---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Inclusive Education | HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives">

<!-- HERO SECTION -->

<section
  class="relative h-[75vh] bg-cover bg-center"
  style="background-image:url('/images/inclusive/inclusive-hero.jpg');"
>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65"></div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center px-8"
  >

    <div class="max-w-5xl text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-300 font-semibold mb-6"
      >

        INCLUSIVE EDUCATION

      </p>

      <h1
        class="text-white font-extrabold leading-tight text-5xl md:text-7xl"
      >

        Learning

        Without

        <span class="text-green-300">

          Barriers

        </span>

      </h1>

      <p
        class="mt-10 text-white text-xl leading-10"
      >

        Every learner deserves the opportunity to learn,
        participate and thrive.

      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-gray-200 text-lg leading-9"
      >

        HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI)
        partners with schools, teachers and sign language
        interpreters to ensure that deaf and
        hard-of-hearing learners actively participate in
        mental wellbeing education, public health,
        Artificial Intelligence (AI) literacy and
        future-ready digital skills.

      </p>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- EVERY LEARNER MATTERS -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Every Learner Matters

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      Inclusive education goes beyond providing access to
      classrooms. It is about ensuring every learner has
      meaningful opportunities to communicate,
      participate, succeed and prepare for the future.
      Through collaboration with educators and sign
      language interpreters, HPCBI creates learning
      environments where every student feels valued,
      supported and empowered.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- STUDENT SUPPORT -->

<section class="pb-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Student Support

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-9 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      We believe that every learner deserves equal
      opportunities to develop confidence, build
      resilience and acquire skills that prepare them for
      life beyond the classroom.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-14 flex justify-center"
    >

      <img
        src="/images/inclusive/student-support.jpg"
        alt="Student Support"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl h-[650px] w-auto max-w-full object-contain"
      />

    </div>
        <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Every child deserves to feel confident, included and
      empowered to achieve their full potential. Through
      tailored support, accessible learning resources and
      collaboration with teachers and sign language
      interpreters, HPCBI helps create learning
      environments where deaf and hard-of-hearing students
      can participate fully in classroom activities and
      future-ready skills development.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- INCLUSIVE LEARNING -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Inclusive Learning

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Inclusive education is about ensuring that every
      learner has equal opportunities to participate,
      communicate and succeed. Our programmes promote
      accessible teaching methods, mental wellbeing,
      digital literacy and collaboration so that no learner
      is left behind.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-16 flex justify-center"
    >

      <img
        src="/images/inclusive/inclusive-hero.jpg"
        alt="Inclusive Learning"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-6xl object-cover"
      />

    </div>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      By working alongside schools, teachers, families and
      interpreters, we help create classrooms where
      diversity is celebrated, communication barriers are
      reduced and every learner has the opportunity to
      thrive academically, socially and emotionally.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- LEARNING THROUGH INTERPRETERS -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Learning Through Interpreters

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Communication should never be a barrier to education.
      During our school outreach programmes, professional
      sign language interpreters work alongside our
      facilitators to ensure that deaf and hard-of-hearing
      students actively participate in every lesson,
      discussion and practical activity.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- INTERPRETER SESSION -->

<section class="pb-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Interpreter Session

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-9 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Sign language interpretation ensures that every
      learner can fully engage with mental wellbeing,
      public health and digital skills training.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-14 flex justify-center"
    >

      <video
        controls
        preload="metadata"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl h-[650px] w-auto max-w-full"
      >

        <source
          src="/videos/inclusive/interpreter-session.mp4"
          type="video/mp4"
        />

      </video>

    </div>
        <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      During every classroom session, our facilitators work
      closely with professional sign language interpreters,
      ensuring that deaf and hard-of-hearing learners can
      confidently participate in discussions, ask questions,
      collaborate with classmates and benefit fully from each
      learning experience.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- INTERPRETER SESSION 2 -->

<section class="pb-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Interpreter Session 2

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-6 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Inclusive learning becomes meaningful when every
      student can communicate, understand and actively
      participate. Our programmes ensure that no learner is
      left behind.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-14 flex justify-center"
    >

      <video
        controls
        preload="metadata"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-5xl"
      >

        <source
          src="/videos/inclusive/interpreter-session2.mp4"
          type="video/mp4"
        />

      </video>

    </div>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Through inclusive teaching approaches, practical
      demonstrations and continuous interaction between
      facilitators, interpreters and teachers, students are
      empowered to develop confidence, improve wellbeing and
      prepare for future opportunities in an increasingly
      digital world.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- WHY INCLUSIVE EDUCATION MATTERS -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8"
  >

    <div class="text-center">

      <h2
        class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Why Inclusive Education Matters

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        Inclusive education transforms lives by ensuring
        every learner has equal opportunities to learn,
        participate and realise their full potential.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🤝

        </div>

        <h3
          class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold"
        >

          Equal Opportunity

        </h3>

        <p
          class="mt-5 leading-8 text-gray-600"
        >

          Every learner deserves equal access to quality
          education and opportunities to succeed.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🧠

        </div>

        <h3
          class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold"
        >

          Mental Wellbeing

        </h3>

        <p
          class="mt-5 leading-8 text-gray-600"
        >

          Supporting confidence, emotional resilience and
          positive mental wellbeing for every learner.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          💻

        </div>

        <h3
          class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold"
        >

          Digital Inclusion

        </h3>

        <p
          class="mt-5 leading-8 text-gray-600"
        >

          Preparing young people with digital and AI skills
          needed for tomorrow's opportunities.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          ❤️

        </div>

        <h3
          class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold"
        >

          Belonging

        </h3>

        <p
          class="mt-5 leading-8 text-gray-600"
        >

          Creating classrooms where every learner feels
          respected, valued and included.

        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>
<!-- HIGHLIGHTS FROM OUR INCLUSIVE EDUCATION PROGRAMME -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Highlights from Our Inclusive Education Programme

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      Every photograph reflects our commitment to creating
      learning environments where every learner has the
      opportunity to participate, communicate and thrive.
      These moments capture our work with students,
      teachers and sign language interpreters as we build
      more inclusive schools across Lagos State.

    </p>

    <h3
      class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-16"
    >

      Highlights from Our Programme

    </h3>

    <p
      class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-9"
    >

      These photographs showcase real classroom moments
      during our inclusive education programme, reflecting
      collaboration, participation and equal learning
      opportunities for every student.

    </p>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16"
    >

      <img
        src="/images/inclusive/classroom1.jpg"
        alt="Inclusive Classroom Session"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer object-cover h-80 w-full"
      />

      <img
        src="/images/inclusive/classroom2.jpg"
        alt="Inclusive Classroom Session"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer object-cover h-80 w-full"
      />

      <img
        src="/images/inclusive/inclusive-hero.jpg"
        alt="Inclusive Learning"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer object-cover h-80 w-full"
      />

      <img
        src="/images/inclusive/student-support.jpg"
        alt="Student Support"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer object-cover h-80 w-full"
      />

    </div>

    <p
      class="mt-12 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-9 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >

      At HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI),
      inclusion is more than a programme—it is a commitment
      to ensuring that every learner, regardless of ability,
      has access to quality education, meaningful
      participation and opportunities to build a brighter
      future.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- OUR IMPACT -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <h2
        class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Our Inclusive Impact

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        Together with schools, teachers and interpreters,
        we are creating learning environments where every
        learner has the opportunity to thrive.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg">

        <div class="text-6xl">

          🏫

        </div>

        <h3 class="text-5xl font-bold text-green-700 mt-6">

          1+

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">

          Special Needs School

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg">

        <div class="text-6xl">

          👨‍🎓

        </div>

        <h3 class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-700 mt-6">

          100+

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">

          Students Reached

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg">

        <div class="text-6xl">

          👩‍🏫

        </div>

        <h3 class="text-5xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mt-6">

          10+

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">

          Teachers Engaged

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg">

        <div class="text-6xl">

          🤝

        </div>

        <h3 class="text-5xl font-bold text-red-700 mt-6">

          100%

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">

          Inclusive Participation

        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIAL -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900">

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <p
      class="text-3xl leading-relaxed text-white italic"
    >

      "Inclusion is not simply about opening classroom
      doors. It is about ensuring every learner is heard,
      respected and empowered to succeed."

    </p>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-green-300 font-bold text-xl"
    >

      HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI)

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- CALL TO ACTION -->

<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-700 py-24">

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-white"
    >

      Support Inclusive Education

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-xl leading-9 text-white"
    >

      Together we can ensure that every learner,
      regardless of disability, has access to quality
      education, mental wellbeing support and future-ready
      digital skills.

    </p>

    <a
      href="/support-our-mission"
      class="inline-block mt-12 bg-white text-green-700 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
    >

      Support Our Mission

    </a>

  </div>

</section>

</Layout>